		<true/>
	</dict>
	<key>NSCameraUsageDescription</key>
	<string>Camera and photo access is required to take photos and record videos, as well as to use video calls and create photo and video content.</string>
	<key>NSLocationWhenInUseUsageDescription</key>
	<string>Geolocation access is required to determine the user's location and provide them with local content.</string>
	<key>NSMicrophoneUsageDescription</key>
	<string>Microphone access is required so users can record voice messages and engage in video chats.</string>
	<key>NSPhotoLibraryUsageDescription</key>
	<string>Camera and photo access is required to take photos and record videos, as well as to use video calls and create photo and video content.</string>
	<key>NSUserTrackingUsageDescription</key>
	<string>We use your data to deliver personalized content and improve user experience.</string>
